{"tid":401783,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人第一次聽某啲歌就覺得好熟","createTime":"2017-09-16T02:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T03:32:03.000Z","uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35ad6d52d3776e5ebb4d81fe0afcac123f5306d7","tid":401783,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:08:13.000Z","msg":"唔係講緊抄歌 通常係啲係身邊比較冷門歌手 所以肯定朋友唔會播<br />\n<br />\n有種好似聽過既feel 瞬間令你覺得細個係 聽過呢個旋律<br />\n係之後發現全隻碟都好似聽過<br />\n有啲似音樂版deja vu<br />\n呢種啲歌通常聽前奏就知副歌你會唔會鍾意"},{"pid":"5523bf6fbca22f8e31a38fb109d420051127cdcd","tid":401783,"uid":2688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:12:38.000Z","msg":"試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該未聽過又覺得好似有d熟"},{"pid":"87197bbdc64f52d8c238a08df38c6497d1efb235","tid":401783,"uid":128563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係講緊抄歌 通常係啲係身邊比較冷門歌手 所以肯定朋友唔會播<br />\n<br />\n有種好似聽過既feel 瞬間令你覺得細個係 聽過呢個旋律<br />\n係之後發現全隻碟都好似聽過<br />\n有啲似音樂版deja vu<br />\n呢種啲歌通常聽前奏就知副歌你會唔會鍾意</blockquote><br />\n因為流行音樂用嘅和弦行進絕大部分都係一樣嘅，基本上可以連埋一齊。所以有時候唱歌唱唱下會唱咗另一首歌。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wxJImbUCyJw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwxJImbUCyJw&d=PwBGKwisCUV%2FBu%2FFbY7d754f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=4be22fdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wxJImbUCyJw</a>"},{"pid":"007f97213de4edc09ee4855404cd3e4864468247","tid":401783,"uid":135067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:33:09.000Z","msg":"花落誰家同落花流水<br />\n唔知點解覺得好似"},{"pid":"a4325362f56768c6af3f0e88cdef4094dd457958","tid":401783,"uid":51559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:51:04.000Z","msg":"青石巷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一次聽個陣好肯定我曾經聽過，但真係諗唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41821ccccc179cd736378f5a47799846083d668b","tid":401783,"u